## v1.0.0 (2026-03-17)

**Initial version.**

**Changed by:** ProjectOdyssey mass rebase session — 138 open PRs, 80+ conflicting
**Verification:** verified-local

### Content
- Batch rebase 100+ conflicting PRs using parallel sub-agents
- `--theirs` strategy for all conflict resolution
- 5-9 parallel agents, 10-12 PRs per batch
- No phased ordering or semantic resolution
- No pixi.lock special handling
- No CI fix integration (Phase 4)
- No handling of closed/superseded PRs
